<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<script type="text/javascript" src="js/Device_rem.js"></script>
	<title>支付确认</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/payment.css" />
	<script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="js/login.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="js/ajaxPayMent.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

	<div id="header">
		<div class="titleArea">
			<span class="prev"><a href="javascript:history.go(-1)">&lt;</a></span>
			<h2>支付确认</h2>
		</div>
	</div>
	 
	<div id="wrap">

		<div id="container">
			<div class="contents">
				<div class="payment">
					<div class="info displaynone">
						<p class="title clearfix"><span class="icon_doctor"></span>急诊 </p>
						<p class="Detailed">三甲医院预约，视频面对面咨询问诊<br/>无障碍直面沟通</p>
						<p class="Total clearfix">支付金额 <strong class="TotalPrice">{$total_price}</strong></p>
					</div>
					<div class="info0 displaynone">
						<p class="title clearfix"><span class="icon_video"></span>视频问诊 </p>
						<p class="Detailed">三甲医院预约，视频面对<br/>无障碍直面沟通</p>
						<p class="Total clearfix">支付金额 <strong class="TotalPrice">{$total}</strong></p>
					</div>
					<div class="info1 displaynone">
						<p class="title clearfix"><span class="icon_tel"></span>电话问诊 </p>
						<p class="Detailed">三甲医院预约，一对一的咨询问诊<br/>沟通快捷方便</p>
						<p class="Total clearfix">支付金额 <strong class="TotalPrice">{$total}</strong></p>
					</div>
					<div class="info2 displaynone">
						<p class="title clearfix"><span class="icon_doctor"></span>私人医生 </p>
						<p class="label">
							<span class="video">{$count}次视频问诊</span>
							<span class="phone">{$telCount}次电话问诊</span>
							<span class="message">留言免费</span>
						</p>
						<p class="Detailed">获得医生的随访<br/>创建个人电子病历</p>
						<p class="Total clearfix">支付金额 <strong class="TotalPrice"><span>{$total}</span> / {$effectTime}天</strong></p>
					</div>
					<div class="infoBox"></div>
					<div class="Price">
						<p class="pay clearfix"><span class="icon_alipay"></span>支付宝支付 <strong class="TotalPrice">></strong></p>
						<p class="Agree clearfix"><span id="check" class="icon_check on"></span>同意<strong> <a href="#paymentAgreement.html">《支付协议》</a></strong></p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div id="footer"></div>
	</div>
	
</body>
</html>